When worlds collide⚡Heading to Chile tomorrow to be on the panel to judge one of the Shredders in my book, @vianezsk8 🇵🇷 I met Vianez back in 2019, she was exuding drive and professionalism as she skated a school at dark, lit only by my handheld light- I asked what her goal was- She said to me, “I want to represent my country in Skateboarding” - And here she is 💫 Watching the evolution of skateboarding unfold before my eyes, gosh it’s just priceless ❤️ Last frame is unpublished art by Vianez herself 🛹🛹 #skateboardingisfun #iloveskateboarding
